title: Miley has lunch date with fiancé Liam Hemsworth
text:
Miley Cyrus enjoyed a casual lunch date with her 'best friend' and fiancé Liam Hemsworth at Malibu modern bistro Ollo on Tuesday.
The 24-year-old pop diva was dressed for the gym in a black Vans hoodie, blue capri leggings, and bright red sneakers.
The Australian 27-year-old looked almost seaworthy in his navy sweater, matching knit beanie, and low-slung grey jeans.

The dog-loving millennials - who fell in love on the 2009 set of The Last Song - confirmed their on/off engagement was back on last March following a two-year split.
'People will figure it out, they already have...They're not dumb,' the Hunger Games alum told GQ Australia last year.
'I guess when I feel something, then I just feel it and I go for it. I make my decisions about what's going to make me happy, what I think is right and what I want to do - and I don't worry too much outside of that.'

The Happy Hippie founder was also among the 750K protesters to take part in the January 21 Women's March in downtown Los Angeles.
'We don't want to talk about change. We want to be the change that we want to see,' Cyrus - who boasts 138.1M followers - announced .

The Grammy and Golden Globe nominee will sit out the 12th season of NBC's The Voice, but has vowed to return to coach the 13th season.
Meanwhile, Liam is currently enjoying an acting hiatus following the dismal critical response from last year's western The Duel and sequel Independence Day: Resurgence.
